                <h3 class="section">About</h3>
                <p>
                    vuln.pub is made by a dude in his basement. The motivation came after his Elastic Search instance got hacked and used in a DDOS attack. There was a two month window between the vulnerability publication and the actual attack. 

                    <br>
                    <br>
                    The problem is often not the vulnerability itself. Vulnerabilities happen and will continue to happen. The problem is that the publication of the vulnerability rarely makes its way back to the user of the vulnerable software. This is what vuln.pub tries to solve. 
                </p>
            </div>
            

